  "text": "We started our investigation by exploring a 3D neighborhood centered on the promoter of the RB1 gene in the 3D structure of chromosome 13 in normal B-cells (GM06990) [CITATION_1] . We retrieved the list of SNPs found in the promoter region of RB1, and in other DNA strands that are not in the immediate sequence neighborhood of RB1 promoter.",
